PrecisOrder (a) authorizing the Minister of Finance to raise money in the 1999- 2000 fiscal year, (b) designating those officials with the Department of Finance or the Bank of Canada who may sign or countersign Government of Canada Securities, and (c) authorizing the Minister to appoint fiscal agents and registrars in this regard.
